  {
   "id": 16,
   "name": "Mira",
   "x": 12,
   "y": 18,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "People1",
    "file": "rtp/People1.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 32,
    "cols": 12,
    "rows": 8,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "action",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "conditional",
     "cond": {
      "kind": "quest",
      "id": "awakening",
      "check": "done"
     },
     "then": [
      {
       "type": "text",
       "text": "Round and round, Awakened. Descend, remember, descend. One of these cycles, we get out.",
       "face": {
        "sheet": "People1",
        "index": 0
       }
      }
     ],
     "else": [
      {
       "type": "conditional",
       "cond": {
        "kind": "quest",
        "id": "awakening",
        "check": "stage",
        "stage": 3
       },
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "…You're back. Of course you are. They always come back — the System makes sure of it.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "You feel it, don't you? You've stood here before. Said these words before. This isn't your first waking, Awakened. It's not anyone's first.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "That's the cycle. The System loops us — wipes us, wakes us, sends us down again. Most never notice. You're starting to.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        },
        {
         "type": "quest",
         "op": "complete",
         "id": "awakening"
        },
        {
         "type": "grantskill",
         "skill": "first_aid"
        },
        {
         "type": "heal",
         "what": "all"
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "Hold onto what you bring back. The still place by the square — the Remembrance — lets you keep it. Each cycle, remember a little more. That's how we break this. Now go — descend again.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        }
       ],
       "else": [
        {
         "type": "conditional",
         "cond": {
          "kind": "quest",
          "id": "awakening",
          "check": "stage",
          "stage": 2
         },
         "then": [
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "Now the hard part, Awakened. There's a fracture below the plaza — the way DOWN. That's what we do here: we descend.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "Down there the System will offer to keep you alive no matter what. Go TETHERED and it won't let you die — but it watches, and watches, until there's not much 'you' left to watch.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "Go UNTETHERED and it lets go. Death is real then. But you stay yourself, and you remember. Lys's brother chose that. …Choose at the fracture. Then come back — if you come back.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          }
         ],
         "else": [
          {
           "type": "conditional",
           "cond": {
            "kind": "quest",
            "id": "awakening",
            "check": "stage",
            "stage": 1
           },
           "then": [
            {
             "type": "text",
             "text": "The crystal's right there in the plaza. It only takes a moment — and it always takes something. Go on.",
             "face": {
              "sheet": "People1",
              "index": 0
             }
            }
           ],
           "else": [
            {
             "type": "text",
             "text": "Easy, now. You just Awakened — the System pulled you up out of the dark, same as everyone in Dawnhearth.",
             "face": {
              "sheet": "People1",
              "index": 0
             }
            },
            {
             "type": "text",
             "text": "Move with the arrows or the pad; press A to speak and to examine. Your menu holds your Status, Supplies, and the meters that keep you alive.",
             "face": {
              "sheet": "People1",
              "index": 0
             }
            },
            {
             "type": "text",
             "text": "It'll offer you the world. Take what you need… but every favor it does you, it watches a little closer. Mind your Surveillance.",
             "face": {
              "sheet": "People1",
              "index": 0
             }
            },
            {
             "type": "text",
             "text": "Go on — touch the crystal in the plaza and let it 'welcome' you properly. Then come back to me.",
             "face": {
              "sheet": "People1",
              "index": 0
             }
            },
            {
             "type": "quest",
             "op": "stage",
             "id": "awakening",
             "stage": 1
            }
           ]
          }
         ]
        }
       ]
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
