  {
   "id": 23,
   "name": "DescentGate",
   "x": 30,
   "y": 34,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "Crystal",
    "file": "rtp/Crystal.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 64,
    "cols": 12,
    "rows": 8,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "action",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "❖ THE FRACTURE — the way DOWN ❖\nA fracture in the air hums where the System thins — a way DOWN, into the dark beneath Dawnhearth. It has no bottom. You go as deep as you can, and climb back out — or you don't."
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "Deepest reached: floor [best]\nAn Alpha guards every fifth floor; the dark only grows hungrier below.\n⚔ fight  ★ elite  ✦ treasure  ☾ refuge  𝕭 Alpha"
    },
    {
     "type": "choice",
     "prompt": "How will you descend?",
     "options": [
      {
       "label": "Tethered",
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "You keep the System close. It will not let you die down there — and it will never stop watching. (Surveillance climbs toward Collection.)"
        },
        {
         "type": "run",
         "op": "start",
         "tethered": true
        },
        {
         "type": "gendungeon"
        }
       ]
      },
      {
       "label": "Untethered",
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "You cut the tether. No hand will catch you — death is real. But the System loses its grip, and you stay yourself. (The off-grid path.)"
        },
        {
         "type": "run",
         "op": "start",
         "tethered": false
        },
        {
         "type": "gendungeon"
        }
       ]
      },
      {
       "label": "Not yet",
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "You step back. The fracture waits."
        }
       ]
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
  {
